OL,3,C'Deeply let down': small business
OL,4,Creduces opening hours due to roadworks
OL,6,FPosting on Facebook, the studio
OL,7,Fexplains: "As a small local business,
OL,8,Fwe feel deeply let down by the
OL,9,Fcontractors and despite assurances,
OL,10,Faccess to our premises has remained
OL,11,Fsporadic at best."
OL,13,FIn response, Phil Ogier from
OL,14,FGuernsey's Roads & Traffic Management
OL,15,FDepartment says: "When we carry out
OL,16,Froad resurfacing, wherever possible,
OL,17,Fwe plan to ensure our contractor
OL,18,Fmaintains access to homes and
OL,19,Fbusinesses, but we also explain if
OL,20,Fthere might be times when access won't
OL,21,Fbe possible.
